Audio_Set (&452C0)
#Prefix Audio_
#Parent Audio_
=>	R0 =	sample rate (or 0 to read)
	R1 =	sample <type>
	R2 = 	number of <channels>
	R3 = 	<bits> per sample
	
<=	R0 =	current sample rate
	R1 = 	current sample type
	R2 =	current channels
	R3 =	current bits

This SWI sets up (or reads) the values for the current data.